        </p>
        <ul
          class="py-2 space-y-[3px] text-sm list-disc list-inside text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400"
        >
          <li>React.js,Vue.js,Svelte Development</li>
          <li>Enterprise Application Development</li>
          <li>Cloud Computing and DevOps</li>
          <li>Website, Desktop and Mobile Development</li>
          <li>and more...</li>
        </ul>
        <Button
          text="Check out my linkedin"
          link="https://www.linkedin.com/in/charles-ssekitto-842a4315b/"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative justify-end w-full mt-10 md:flex md:pl-10 md:w-1/2 md:mt-0 md:translate-y-4 xl:translate-y-0"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/images/chucky profile-modified.png"
